## Rollback Plan

If issues arise post-publish, rollback steps:

```bash
# Deprecate published version (marks as deprecated, not removed)
npm deprecate @seanchatmangpt/pictl@latest "Deprecated: See latest"
npm deprecate wasm4pm@latest "Deprecated: See latest"

# Users still can install latest if needed (with warning)
# Publish latesta or latest with fixes

# For catastrophic issues only: unpublish (only within 72 hours)
npm unpublish @seanchatmangpt/pictl@latest --force
```

